h2(class='heading-medium') Progressive collapsibles


p Building accessible, collapsible content sections from basic flow.


div(class='example')

  
  section(aria-labelledby='messages')
  
  
    h2(class='heading-large' id='messages') Messages
    
    
    p You have 2 new messages.
  
  
    div(class='collapsible')
    
      div(class='collapsible-item')
      
        div(class='collapsible-heading')
          h3(class='bold-medium') You have been given access to Agri Agents Ltd
      
        div(class='collapsible-content')
          div(class='text')
            p John Smith has given you permission to view and amend information about this business and make applications on their behalf.
      
      
      div(class='collapsible-item')
      
        div(class='collapsible-heading')
          h3(class='bold-medium') Welcome to Rural Payments
      
        div(class='collapsible-content')
          div(class='text')
            p Fusce a risus libero. Nam risus purus, pharetra eget porttitor in, dictum ut enim. In auctor, purus vitae luctus tempor.
            
        
pre(aria-hidden='true' role='presentation')
  code(class='language-markup')
